track_notes:
A nice summit with a fantastic view over the caldera and to TF-001. Several shelters and a wide summit area. 
The track is well defined and marked. There are several options in the final part. Avoid to get off the track to the North - it is a long way down to the caldera ...
Navigation could be a problem, clouds and fog can build up very quickly.

Start at the parador hotel and infocentre. Depending on time parking can be challenging at times.
Follow the marked trail and signposts to Alto de Guajara.
There are stone walls at summit as wind protection. 
Plenty of space for antennas. But be mindful as it is a popular summit.
track_title: Loop hike - traverse - from hotel parador
